<span id="freeTextContainer13543164648099130328">An excellent reasonably quick read by author Ira Levin. I had previously watched the film many years ago and couldn&apos;t quite remember in detail but it did not stop my enjoyment at all. Ira Levin has written so many classic novels that have been turned into film blockbusters &apos;Stepford Wives&apos; &apos;Rosemary&apos;s baby&apos; and this is one more. An interesting plot and great descriptive writing that brings the book to life.</span>
  <span id="freeText13543164648099130328" style="display:none">An excellent reasonably quick read by author Ira Levin. I had previously watched the film many years ago and couldn't quite remember in detail but it did not stop my enjoyment at all. Ira Levin has written so many classic novels that have been turned into film blockbusters 'Stepford Wives' 'Rosemary's baby' and this is one more. An interesting plot and great descriptive writing that brings the book to life.</span>
