        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2204485798" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15253728256746638409"><i>
  <b>
    <blockquote>“Do you kill the Nazis when you catch them?” the boy asked.<br/>“No,” Liebermann said.<br/>“Why not?”<br/>“It’s against the law. Besides, it’s better to put them on trial. That way more people learn about them.”<br/>“Learn what?” The boy looked skeptical.<br/>“Who they were, what they did.”<blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>
  </b>
</i></span>

          </span>
        </div>


